<h5 data-zesty-id="content:text:25:9">Connect with Us</h5>
<p data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:26:88">
	Follow "The Salvation Army Women's Auxiliary of Greenville, SC" @GVLWomensAux&nbsp;on&nbsp;<a href="https://www.facebook.com/GVLWomensAux" target="">Facebook</a>.&nbsp;
</p>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:27:66"></div>
<p data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:28:66">
	Follow "Greenville Women's Auxiliary" @gvlwomensaux on&nbsp;<a href="https://www.instagram.com/gvlwomensaux/" target="">Instagram</a>.&nbsp;
</p>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:29:38"></div>
<h5 data-zesty-id="content:text:32:73">Donate</h5>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:33:65">
	When you make a financial contribution to The Women's Auxiliary of Greenville, your donation will be used to help your neighbors receive the help that they need.&nbsp;By mail at: The Salvation Army Women's Auxiliary | PO Box 1237 Greenville, SC, 29602.&nbsp;Click the red button below&nbsp;to donate online.
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;" class="cta-button-group d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 my-3 justify-content-center" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:34:64"><a href="https://give.salvationarmycarolinas.org/give/389338/#!/donation/checkout" class="btn btn-primary gap-1 mt-2">Donate to SAWA</a></p>
